When formulated as a mouthwash or spray, benzydamine may be used to treat traumatic conditions like pharyngitis following tonsillectomy or the use of a naso-gastric tube, inflammatory conditions like pharyngitis, aphthous ulcers and oral ulceration due to radiation therapy, dentistry operations and procedures, or more general conditions like sore throat, sore tongue, sore gums, mouth ulcers, or discomfort caused by dentures. [L1121] 
When used as a topical cream, benzydamine may be employed to relieve symptoms associated with painful inflammatory conditions of the muscolo-skeletal system including acute inflammatory disorders such as myalgia and bursitis or traumatic conditions like sprains, strains, bruises, sore muscles, stiff joints, or even the after-effects of fractures. [ L1123]', '6221032241009', '', 974, '2024-11-08', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(29232, 'Viasalmol plus 200 doses inh. spray', 'فياسالمول بلس 200 جرعة بخاخ سبراي استنشاق', '50.5', '72', 'Beclomethasone+salbutamol', 'Mdi pharma', 'Spray', 'بخاخ', 'موسع قصبي سريع المفعول، حيث يعمل عن طريق فتح ممرات التنفس، وإرخاء العضلات، يستخدم لتخفيف بعض الأعراض المزعجة التي قد تعوق المريض عن ممارسة أنشطته اليومية، مثل: التشنج القصبي', 'Bronchodilator.glucocorticoid steroid and short-acting b2 agonist', '', '-beclomethasone dipropionate 50 mcg -salbutamol 100 mcg', '6224002249074', '', 12449, '2025-01-15', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
