(8046, 'No-wawa diaper cream 75 gm', 'نو واوا كريم حفاضات 75 جم', '', '115', 'Zinc oxide+beeswax+chamomile+panthenol', 'Meduva pharma', 'Cream', 'كريم', '', 'Diaper rash', '75 gm', 'Zinc can be used for the treatment and prevention of zinc deficiency/its consequences, including stunted growth and acute diarrhea in children, and slowed wound healing. It is also utilized for boosting the immune system, treating the common cold and recurrent ear infections, as well as preventing lower respiratory tract infections [L2172].', '', '', 765, '2025-11-17', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
